Company Profile
Sector: Financials
Industry: Banking
Sub-Industry: Banks
Allegiance Bancshares, Inc. operates as a bank holding company. The Company, through its subsidiaries, offers banking products and services such as certificate of deposit, money market accounts, business and personal loans, treasury management, savings accounts, and online banking services.




