Allegiance Bank is a full-service Houston community bank focused on providing banking services primarily for small to medium-sized business owners and individuals in the greater Houston area and to their employees, families and friends.
If you're looking for a bank that treats you as a valued customer, you've come to the right place!  At Allegiance Bank, we go beyond a promise to a pledge.  A pledge to do all we can to ensure your success.
How?  By providing value and extraordinary personalized service to not only our customers, but also to our employees, shareholders, and the community.  Plus, we focus on establishing long-term relationships and recognize that each customer is unique.  Simply put, your small to medium-sized business banking needs are our biggest priority.
If you haven't already, we invite you to visit one of our 16 Houston locations  

